
  Grovyle    Grass Type Pokémon

  The leaves growing out of GROVYLE’s 
  body are convenient for camouflaging 
  it from enemies in the forest. 
   Grovyle is a master at 
  climbing trees in jungles. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Treecko ► Grovyle ► Sceptile

